				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/C%E1%BA%A3nh-%E1%BA%A3o-ti%C3%AAn-c%C3%B4-ph%C3%BA/poem-kymAnakZvCTDb9itxi_3WQ">Cảnh ảo tiên cô phú - 警幻仙姑賦</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Tuy%E1%BA%BFt-C%E1%BA%A7n/author-1DK3jrzNRQ6A5gusK7iSPw">Tào Tuyết Cần</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/D%C4%A9-k%C3%ADnh-t%E1%BA%B7ng-bi%E1%BB%87t/poem-HbgK3vKm_kodDFAsVgQ2Xw">Dĩ kính tặng biệt - 以鏡贈別</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/D%E1%BB%A5c-Thu%C3%BD-s%C6%A1n-Linh-T%E1%BA%BF-th%C3%A1p-k%C3%BD/poem-RqBdsePEcszTQ2nOSenukg">Dục Thuý sơn Linh Tế tháp ký - 浴翠山靈濟塔記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-H%C3%A1n-Si%C3%AAu/author-8OezdZDSC-q-9wfu_BOuVw">Trương Hán Siêu</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/%C4%90%E1%BB%81-ho%E1%BA%A1-mai/poem-xOogqNjbaXknquxnAP16aQ">Đề hoạ mai - 題畫梅</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-Mi%E1%BB%87n/author-fEGcjpEMDS77hLL_7VN-Wg">Vương Miện</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/Hoa-Nh%E1%BB%8B-phu-nh%C3%A2n-c%E1%BB%91-tr%E1%BA%A1ch-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-JQKjW7a9C9mlYemcO2_9dA">Hoa Nhị phu nhân cố trạch kỳ 2 - 花蕊夫人故宅其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/U%C3%B4ng-Nguy%C3%AAn-L%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng/author-HbKyCtS3WFreEebdROalkQ">Uông Nguyên Lượng</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhung-D%E1%BB%A5c/Ho%C3%A0-phi%C3%AAn/poem-eZp0oNv7oqgNku53eDwWGA">Hoà phiên - 和蕃</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nhung-D%E1%BB%A5c/author-lGQuf2FjmcyE81PnImQFVA">Nhung Dục</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/Thai-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-di-s%E1%BB%B1/poem-QdADUUqIuccobnxI7pw9DA">Thai Dương di sự - 邰陽遺事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Ng%C3%B4-Th%C3%AC-Nh%E1%BA%ADm/author-14GcnhLjD2ajP0MTgtX13Q">Ngô Thì Nhậm</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%C3%ADn-h%C3%A0nh-vi%E1%BB%85n-tu-thu%E1%BB%B7-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng/poem-GtdmSoi6EuIHKcwHFkRN8g">Tín hành viễn tu thuỷ đồng - 信行遠修水筒</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/T%E1%BB%B1-qu%C3%A2n-chi-xu%E1%BA%A5t-h%E1%BB%B9-k%E1%BB%B3-03/poem-AM6YbmAQNpWyP_2o4393zg">Tự quân chi xuất hỹ kỳ 03 - 自君之出矣其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Thanh-T%C3%A2m-t%C3%A0i-nh%C3%A2n/author-Ry0GXj_uifS6AejvZUIukQ">Thanh Tâm tài nhân</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-Long/Y%C3%AAn-Kinh-t%E1%BB%A9c-s%E1%BB%B1/poem--FdHTbHtY7ZfyS-XKBO56Q">Yên Kinh tức sự - 燕京即事</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%93-Long/author--9TnyXqqJ0jrOvcw26zfjw">Đồ Long</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
